{"title":"Food. ","clock":false,"countdown":0,"intro":{"buttons":{"start":"Start"},"content":[]},"activity":{"scenes":[{"block":"scene","name":"SC1","countdown":0,"instructions":{"open":true,"content":[{"block":"group","class":"flex gap-2 items-center","content":[{"block":"audio","class":"","file":"files/B1-1U2L4EA-INS.mp3","wave":false,"autoplay":false,"id":"","name":"wo5Z"},{"block":"text","class":"","text":"Read the next paragraph about Jorge´s father's trip to Mexico and his experience with the local food. ","id":"","name":"2aXX"}]}]},"content":[{"block":"group","class":"bg-slate-100 rounded p-3 my-2 max-w-5xl mx-auto","content":[{"marker":"","class":" m-20 bg-orange-500 pr-2 rounded-lg","content":[{"marker":"","class":"bg-yellow-50 pr-2 rounded-lg","content":[{"marker":"","class":"text-2xl  bg-orange-500 pr-2 rounded-lg","content":[{"marker":"","class":"bg-yellow-50 p-20 rounded-lg","content":[{"block":"text","class":"","text":"When I traveled to Mexico, one of the things I enjoyed the most was the food. I visited three different regions and in all three, the variety was plenty. Lots of flavors and combinations. Several ways of making dishes with tortilla, for example. ","name":"owlf","hidden":false,"id":"cuzP"},{"marker":"","class":"bg-yellow-50 p-20 rounded-lg","content":[{"file":"files/B1-1U2L4EA-IMG-01.jpg","class":"mask mask-squircle","id":"P6O5","block":"image","name":"tOGy"}],"background":"","id":"ZZjmCivh","block":"group","name":"R3R3"},{"marker":"","class":"grid grid-cols-2 gap-5","content":[{"block":"text","class":"","text":"Some of them use chicken, others only a few vegetables like lettuce, tomatoes and onions. But all of them use “salsa”, which is a blend of peppers, garlic, coriander, a little onion, salt and some water. ","name":"Dhpr","hidden":false,"id":"T0YAa0M7"},{"file":"files/B1-1U2L4EA-IMG-02.jpg","class":"mask mask-squircle","id":"c7hW","block":"image","name":"7REG"}],"background":"","id":"FrHb","block":"group","name":"VfSm"},{"marker":"","class":"my-2","content":[{"block":"text","class":"","text":"After that you decide if you put in a lot of salsa or just a little, depending on how much you enjoy the spicy flavors.","name":"VfOe","hidden":false,"id":"9IH2dtNR"}],"background":"","id":"9tOX","block":"group","name":"Eo9K"},{"marker":"","class":"my-2","content":[{"block":"text","class":"","text":"They also have many kinds of fruits, some that I have never seen before. All kinds of vegetables and plenty more forms to prepare them. I have never tasted so many ways of mixed ingredients and they all tasted so good. Definitely I will be back in a few months and visit other regions to find out more and more cooking recipes and flavors.","name":"LrCn","hidden":false,"id":"Rs1Rjsb2"},{"marker":"","class":"flex justify-center my-10","content":[{"file":"files/B1-1U2L4EA-IMG-03.jpg","class":"mask mask-squircle w-3/4","id":"yQZw","block":"image","name":"0c5T"}],"background":"","id":"MsEE","block":"group","name":"2Uyj"}],"background":"","id":"hnHV","block":"group","name":"Uv1l"}],"background":"","id":"eQYipp47","block":"group","name":"T4ho"}],"background":"","id":"38y0","block":"group","name":"ClVu"}],"background":"","id":"GRdQVHJl","block":"group","name":"GgdH"}],"background":"","id":"Emva","block":"group","name":"xyej"},{"block":"text","class":"","text":"Activity content...","name":"3Ovd","hidden":false}],"background":"","name":"4Cs6","hidden":false,"marker":"","id":""},{"symbol":"FinalizeGroup"}],"id":""}]},"end":{"buttons":{"restart":false},"content":[{"symbol":"finishedAll"}]},"symbols":{"finishedAll":{"class":"w-full","content":[{"block":"group","class":"bg-slate-100 rounded p-5 text-center w-full","content":[{"block":"text","text":"Congratulations, you finished the activity.","class":"","name":"Congra"}],"background":"","name":"CongraGroup"},{"block":"group","class":"text-center p-5","content":[{"block":"finished","name":"finishedBlock"}],"background":"","name":"finishedGroup"}],"background":"","block":"grou